# Generated SQL migration files live here. Populated by
#
#   cd agent && npx drizzle-kit generate --config=./drizzle.config.ts
#
# The runtime path uses these via `runMigrations()` in
# `agent/db/migrate.ts` — Drizzle Kit tracks applied migrations in
# `__drizzle_migrations` so re-running is a no-op. Commit every
# generated file alongside its `meta/_journal.json` update.